result.adr_address: 香港馬鞍山西沙路628號
result.name: 居食屋「和民」

reviews.text:
店內環境清幽，裝潢別緻樓底高，座位寛敞舒適。
服務員態度殷勤，招待周到。
餐具準備充足，整潔衛生。
菜式種類及追加小食繁多，提供日替(按周一至日)不同的午餐 及 2，3，4人前(2，3，4人食用份量) 選擇。
飲品由地道的檸檬荼/水，奶荼 到 富日本料理 特色的飲品均有提供。
價錢方面由40-400不等，無論自己想舒服食番餐，定同一家大細享受美食，都係唔錯的選擇。

The shop is comfortable and quite . Large sites and table with more than enough space for you to enjoy the food.
The waiter and waitress are very friendly and dedicated. Tools are well prepared and hygienic.
There are more than 10 types of main cause and 20 types of small dishes for you to choose.
Lemon water and juice , milk tea and classical Japan  drinks are also provided. 
The price are ranged from 40 to 400 more.
食物凍渣 侍應生服務態度差 收費偏貴 物非所值
yummy food, not too crowded. Great fusion cuisine.
The food is amazing. It provides a large variety for you to choose from,from salad, sushi, pizza to shabu shabu and teriyaki. It is certainly worth trying
麵很細碗，麵質差，飯的份量也很少，餸很少，炒菜也是很少很少，完全不能接受
